snippet.title: Need For Speed - High Stakes (PS1) 100% Longplay
snippet.description:
This longplay goes through a 100% playthrough of Need For Speed: High Stakes on the Playstation 1. First, I start by completing all the Tournament and Special Events, then I move on to playing through several iterations of the Hot Pursuit mode to unlock cop cars and the bonus helicopter.


TIMELINE

00:00 Intro
04:00 Worldwide Roadster Classic
23:49 Weekend Road Racing Classic
36:24 Twilight Open Series
54:29 Regional Club Circuit
1:16:51 International Open Road Tour
1:40:05 Super Sedan Challenge
2:08:05 Grand Touring Competition
2:41:29 Corvette Pro Cup
3:02:41 Knockout Challenge
3:28:13 International Supercar Series
4:04:16 Porsche Pro Cup
4:25:10 Open Road Knockout Challenge
4:39:54 GT Racing Championship
5:03:30 Endurance Racing Championship
6:04:44 Demonstration of Titan
6:10:06 Hot Purusit - Caprice
6:19:33 Hot Pursuit - Corvette
6:30:25 Hot Pursuit - BMW M5
6:40:54 Hot Pursuit - Porsche 911
6:51:39 Hot Pursuit - Diablo GT
7:02:26 Demonstration of Helicopter
7:07:53 Credits
